  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong><br /><br /></p><ul><li><p>Handle customer inquiries and requests through various channels (phone, email, chat, or in person)</p></li><li><p>Provide accurate information and assistance in a professional manner</p></li><li><p>Process customer requests, updates, and related documentation</p></li><li><p>Maintain and update records in internal systems</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with internal teams to resolve issues and ensure timely follow-up</p></li><li><p>Adhere to company policies, procedures, and service standards</p></li><li><p>Perform other administrative or operational duties as assigned<br /></p><p><br /><a href=\"https://employer.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/jobs/contract-finance-executive-hynt-recruit-express-4b362a49692dfbac3e98a5394fa8f6f4/view#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Please send your resume to rehealth@recruitexpress.com.sg.</a></p><p>We regret to inform you that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>Chloe Impens| Outsourcing Team<br />EA License Number: 99C4599<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd | Company Reg. No. 199601303W</p></li></ul>",
